sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User / Frontend<br/>3000/TCP HTTP
    participant API as ml-pipeline API Server<br/>8888/TCP REST · 8887/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432 TCP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Argo as Argo Workflows<br/>Controller
    participant Driver as ml-pipeline-driver<br/>(Argo task pod)
    participant MLMD as ML Metadata<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant Cache as Cache Service<br/>(via API Server gRPC)
    participant Launcher as ml-pipeline-launcher<br/>(Argo task pod)
    participant S3 as MinIO/S3<br/>9000/TCP HTTP
    participant PA as Persistence Agent<br/>(background)

    Note over User,PA: Flow 1: Pipeline Run Execution

    User->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/runs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    API->>DB: Store run metadata<br/>Username/Password
    API->>K8s: Submit Argo Workflow CR<br/>ServiceAccount
    K8s-->>Argo: Workflow created

    Note over Argo,Launcher: Per-step execution (v2 engine)

    Argo->>Driver: Create driver task pod<br/>ServiceAccount
    Driver->>MLMD: Resolve inputs from context<br/>gRPC (no auth)
    Driver->>Cache: Check execution fingerprint<br/>gRPC · Bearer Token

    alt Cache Hit
        Driver->>MLMD: Fetch cached outputs<br/>gRPC
        Driver->>MLMD: Publish CACHED execution<br/>gRPC
        Note over Driver: Skip launcher — return cached result
    else Cache Miss
        Driver-->>Argo: Pod spec patch (launcher config)
        Argo->>Launcher: Create launcher task pod<br/>ServiceAccount
        Launcher->>S3: Download input artifacts<br/>Access Key + Secret Key
        Note over Launcher: Execute user container code
        Launcher->>S3: Upload output artifacts + logs<br/>Access Key + Secret Key
        Launcher->>MLMD: Record execution results<br/>gRPC
        Launcher->>Cache: Create cache entry<br/>gRPC · Bearer Token
    end

    Note over PA,API: Async state synchronization

    PA->>K8s: Watch Workflow resources<br/>Informer · ServiceAccount
    K8s-->>PA: Workflow status events
    PA->>API: Report execution state<br/>gRPC 8887 · Bearer Token (projected SA)

    Note over User,PA: Flow 2: Scheduled Pipeline Execution

    User->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/recurringruns<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    API->>K8s: Create ScheduledWorkflow CR<br/>ServiceAccount
    Note over K8s: SWF Controller watches CRD
    K8s->>API: Create run on schedule<br/>gRPC 8887 · Bearer Token (projected SA)
    API->>K8s: Submit Argo Workflow<br/>ServiceAccount
